Package com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.ha

The com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.ha package provides interfaces to manage the vCenter Server Inventory Cluster HA settings.

Package com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.ha Description

The com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.ha package provides interfaces to manage the vCenter Server Inventory Cluster HA settings.
